## DBchapter(Operational amplifiers)
## DBsection(Fundamental op-amp circuits)
## KEYWORDS('op amp','dc','circuits')
## TitleText1('Basic Engineering Circuit Analysis')
## EditionText1('8e')
## AuthorText1('Irwin and Nelms')
## Section1('4.3')
